title: Remote Sensing Learning Diary
text:
Preface
This is a Learning Diary for CASA0023 Remotely Sensing Cities and Environment module.
This website contains summary of learning material each week with structures below:
1. Content
2. Summary
3. Applications
4. Reflection
5. Conclusion






Note



You can click the “-\>” button below for the next chapter!
